data.description: MOTIVATED. Welcome to special living at this prestigious development. Nestled within a golf course community, this exquisite villa offers the perfect blend of convenience and leisure. Immaculately maintained and ready to move into, this property promises a lifestyle like no other. Conveniently located in the heard of Palm Beach Gardens, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Healthcare facilities are a short distance away ensuring your every need is met. The property s close to major transportation hubs making community a breeze. This villa is light and airy and has a wonderful screened patio with nice gardens surrounding it. The two car garage is a plus and the roof is brand new. Don't miss this opportunity. This will sell quickly. Community pool is steps away.
